relation: Darrow4 - #50 While the group learn a new dance number, there is someone who is far from happy about it. Never try to steal the funk unless you're ready to handle a nasty proverbial dunk.

Darrow4 - #51 While Poo takes a great initiative in dealing with the shattered foe, he fails to notice the pincer attack Scarabian mummies are famous for. ...Or was that their soup? Well, their soup is pretty delicious, too, in any case.
Darrow4 - #52 Although Poo considers himself an army of one, there are still three more people willing to fight. After breaking into two groups, the battle begins.

Darrow4 - #53 Although the group may be used to crazy battles and random monsters, most people are not so used to the crazier side of things. Still, some handle it well...while others most definitely do not.
